Package dev.innate.util

Class BrewBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.innate.util.BrewBuilder
  • public class BrewBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides a fluent interface for creating an instance of Brew. All of the fields correspond to the available fields of an instance of Brew, and every method (except build) returns the instance of the builder it was called on, allowing for method chaining. Once all of the desired fields have been set, calling build() returns an instance of Brew with those fields populated with the specified values.
